OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe morning will begin cloudy
OL,6,Fwith persistent rain. This rain will
OL,7,Fturn to the occasional shower over
OL,8,FShetland by midday and over Orkney by
OL,9,Fmid-afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FClear spells will increase
OL,12,Fform the evening but these will be
OL,13,Finterspersed with showers, these
OL,14,Fbecoming more frequent towards the
OL,15,Fmorning.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FBright spells and scattered
OL,18,Fshowers at first. The showers clear
OL,19,Ffrom the south as cloud spreads north
OL,20,Fduring the morning. Gales and rain
OL,21,Fwill follow over Orkney by the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
