OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHeavy
OL,6,Frain, hill snow and severe gales clear
OL,7,FSunday morning, leaving a few
OL,8,Fafternoon showers. Mostly dry but
OL,9,Fcloudy Monday and Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
